title: Futurama Complete Season 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 480p 720p TinyMP4
description:
Futurama Season 1-7 - TinyMP4

An attempt to bring great quality with smaller file sizes!

Video: MPEG4 x264
Audio: MPEG4 FAAC

Season 1-4 SD
Resolution: 800x600
Filtered/Upscaled DVD Rips.

Season 5 HD
Resolution: 1280x720
BDRips of the four movies.

Season 6-7 HD
Resolution: 1280x720
Combination BDRips and Web-DL.

Includes Specials: The Lost Adventure, Everybody Loves Hypnotoad, Futurama Live!

- Season numbering scheme is based on production seasons, NOT broadcast order.
- Files are about as small as they can be without a huge quality loss (+/- 5-10%).
- Sizes vary: videos are encoded at a constant quality and not a constant size.
- Some attempt was made to normalize the audio volume level across all episodes.
- If you want the absolute best definitive quality, this torrent is not for you.
- There are two samples: SD and HD to see if this torrent is for you.

If you prefer the episodes in "Season" folders, rename file "CreateFolders.txt" to "CreateFolders.bat". Copy to directory with episodes and run it. TPB would not allow batch files in the video category so I had to upload it as a text file.
